WRITING.TITLE: My favorite goose has these living on her :\

WRITING.TEXT: This bug is roughly 3 mm in length (1/8th inch) Geese are located in eastern Canada.

WRITING.TITLE: I am Doug, King of Geese! I've been visiting them for a couple years, they're usually happy to see me, but I have never seen so many of them move so fast.

I am Doug, King of Geese! This is the flock of geese I visit nearly daily at a small pond in the downtown of my city. Hope it is as much an oasis for your day as it is to our city. Sullivan's goose on youtube if you want to see more. We had a gosling this year, whos life I've been documenting :)
